      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "<a id=\"_Toc492473347\">H 14670</a> – A number of our companions, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad Bin Khalid, from Muhammad Bin Ali, from Nuh Bin Shuayb, from the one whom he mentioned:",
          "<span class=\"first-chapter-phrase\"><span class=\"first-in-chapter character-a\">A</span>bu Al-Hassan</span><sup>asws</sup> said: ‘The one who’s water of the back (semen) has changed, so the butter milk and the honey would be beneficial for him’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "222. A number of our companions, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad Bin Khalid, from Muhammad Bin Ali, from Nuh Bin Shuayb, from the one whom he mentioned: Abu Al-Hassan (a.s.) said: ‘The one who’s water of the back (semen) has changed, so the butter milk and the honey would be beneficial for him’."
        ]
